<Infographic
  title="Cisco × Qunnect Brooklyn–Manhattan metro entanglement-swap"
  description="First metro-scale entanglement-swapping demonstration over deployed commercial telecom fibre. Three-node hub-and-spoke topology spanning 17.6 km of New York City underground fibre, with the Bell-state-measurement hub at 60 Hudson Street and two warm-rubidium Qunnect Carina sources at the Brooklyn spokes. Announced 18 February 2026."
  references={[
